    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail reflects a standard of maintenance that will satisfy the most discerning automotive enthusiast. From the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, this unit represents the definitive pinnacle of its class. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an automobile of uncompromising integrity and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
