    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning factory paint which remains free of swirls, rock chips, or any surface imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and the original high-gloss trim is pristine. Every electronic feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the driver-assist technologies, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history and remarkably low mileage. It has been strictly adult-driven, never seen inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this collector-grade example offers a rare opportunity to own a like-new masterpiece without the new-car depreciation.",
